Who I Am

MORE THAN A TRAINER.
YOUR FITNESS PARTNER.

I'm Ravi Raj Bhagora, born and raised in the heart of Dahod, Gujarat. Fitness isn't just my profession — it's my calling. I believe every body has the potential for greatness, and I'm here to unlock it. With years of hands-on experience and deep knowledge of diet, nutrition, and exercise science, I create personalized plans that don't just change your body — they change your life.

What sets me apart? I don't believe in shortcuts or crash diets. I believe in sustainable transformation — building habits that last a lifetime. Whether you're a beginner taking your first step or an athlete pushing for peak performance, I meet you where you are and take you where you want to go.

Expert Knowledge

FUEL YOUR BODY
THE RIGHT WAY

Ravi doesn't just train bodies — he educates minds. With deep knowledge of macronutrients, micronutrients, and Indian dietary science, he crafts nutrition plans that are as delicious as they are effective. No boring boiled chicken here — think smart desi meals optimized for your fitness goals.

🥚
Protein Optimization
Strategic protein timing using paneer, dal, eggs, chicken, and whey to maximize muscle protein synthesis throughout the day.
🍚
Smart Carb Cycling
Roti, rice, and oats timed around your workouts. High-carb on training days, controlled on rest days for optimal body composition.
🥑
Healthy Fats & Micros
Ghee, nuts, and seeds for hormone health. Complete vitamin and mineral planning for energy and recovery.
💧
Hydration & Supplements
Science-backed supplementation guidance. No unnecessary spending — only what your body actually needs.
